@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
}

<div class="bm-page-header">
    <h1 class="h2">Privacy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-0">How MatchPAS handles information in this demo application.</p>
</div>

<div class="bm-card border-0 p-4 p-md-5">
    <h2 class="h5">Data we store</h2>
    <p class="text-muted">Account details (email, display name), proposal content, research areas, and match records. Administrators can list matches for oversight.</p>
    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">Blind review</h2>
    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Until a supervisor confirms a match, supervisors do not see student identity in the review workflow. After confirmation, both parties can see each other as designed by your institution.</p>
</div>
